# Coffee Shop Project

A simple Python project modeling a coffee shop using three classes (**Customer**, **Coffee**, **Order**) along with optional SQL and test files. This project demonstrates object-oriented programming concepts such as attributes, instance methods, class relationships, and data validation, as well as basic SQL schema design.

